{"tid":1818502,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Ｘmen的「野獸」－尼古拉斯·霍爾特確定將會加入新一部《職業特工隊》電影！","createTime":"2020-01-10T03:12:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T00:51:24.000Z","uid":117117,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b8350e727723cdd8a39ae51bd7ce28a2e64ee091","tid":1818502,"uid":117117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:12:32.000Z","msg":"之前「卡特幹員」海莉&middot;艾特沃（Hayley Atwell）以及「螳螂女」龐&middot;克萊門捷夫（Pom Klementieff）之後，第三個飾演漫威英雄的演員「野獸」－尼可拉斯&middot;霍特（Nicholas Hoult）也將加入知名動作諜報作品－《不可能的任務》（Mission Impossible）電影其演出。<br />\n<br />\n當然老樣子，導演克里斯多福&middot;麥奎里（Christopher McQuarrie）仍在自己社交平台貼上尼可拉斯&middot;霍特參予的照片，推測他將會飾演反派，不過其餘的詳細設定並沒有公開。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LU3MaSa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLU3MaSa.jpg&h=3d8754a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《不可能的任務》第七集和第八集被公布分別在 2021 年和 2022 年發布，並計畫一同進行拍攝，而除了湯姆&middot;克魯斯（Tom Cruise）所飾演的主角－伊森&middot;韓特（Ethan Hunt）會回歸外，蕾貝卡&middot;弗格森（Rebecca Ferguson）也將重新扮演伊爾莎&middot;佛斯特（Ilsa Faust）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ntom cruise 將當初有份爭做goose 個仔既3位男演員都派哂角比佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5098c8d53f73e0a4f9cf239c5350ee94b1ff67f","tid":1818502,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:12:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d001c1a90c13f4708f1e340c3e224b5c67fb6a16","tid":1818502,"uid":68689,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:31:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=3gf9dq1/ctp-vzntr/1528977633800sp3404sr42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D3gf9dq1%2Fctp-vzntr%2F1528977633800sp3404sr42.jpg&h=1ef550e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGotg既螳螂女好似苑瓊丹"},{"pid":"d7523a3910c89819b0b91dcfaa4b808c90dbcfcd","tid":1818502,"uid":183758,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20